{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01HYMDVoXmhfto1cy3RCF66c","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_016EEdvFzDbzatJj1wKST9FT","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/src/commands/AGENTS.md","old_string":"### verify-env.ts","new_string":"### stats.ts\nAnalyzes token consumption and cost from ralph session logs. Parses JSONL log files for streaming API events, aggregates by phase (create-story, dev-story, code-review, verify, retro), story, tool, and date. Computes API-equivalent cost using Opus 4.6 pricing. Formats human-readable markdown report.\n- **Key deps:** `lib/output` (info, ok, fail, jsonOutput), node:fs, commander\n- **Subcommands:** none; supports `--save` (write report to cost-report.md), `--json`\n\n### verify-env.ts"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":206,"cache_read_input_tokens":58016,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":206},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2e5d4728-d8cb-4df9-909c-e75227099f62","uuid":"9f70f676-3f0b-4392-a7c7-4baf887f3dc4"}
